snippet.title: Density Experiment Trailer - April 2021
snippet.description:
Density Experiment is a puzzle platformer created as a student project by Tim Drew (Red Squirrel Games) & Cameron Callaghan.

Download now from itch.io! https://redsquirrelgames.itch.io/density-experiment

Lead Programmer - Cameron Callaghan
Additional Programming - Tim Drew
Music, Art & Level Design - Tim Drew
